### Swiss Transport API - Test Requests
### Base URL: http://transport.opendata.ch/v1

### 1. Find nearest station by coordinates (Home location)
GET http://transport.opendata.ch/v1/locations?x=47.41729671900619&y=9.357221339051806

###

### 2. Get stationboard for a specific station (example: using station ID)
# First run the locations request above, then use a station ID from the response
# Example station IDs: 8506302 (St. Gallen), 8503000 (Z端rich HB)
GET http://transport.opendata.ch/v1/stationboard?id=8506302&limit=10

###

### 3. Get stationboard with more results
GET http://transport.opendata.ch/v1/stationboard?id=8506302&limit=20

###

### 4. Search for stations by name
GET http://transport.opendata.ch/v1/locations?query=St.Gallen,Vonwil

###

### 5. Get connections between two locations
# From St. Gallen to Z端rich HB
GET http://transport.opendata.ch/v1/connections?from=St.Gallen&to=Z端rich

###

### 6. Get connections with specific datetime
GET http://transport.opendata.ch/v1/connections?from=St.Gallen&to=Z端rich&date=2026-01-02&time=14:00

###

### 7. Find stations near coordinates (alternative format)
GET http://transport.opendata.ch/v1/locations?x=47.4172&y=9.3572&type=station

###

